Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.71,0:00:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗噗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.29,0:00:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法師要是沒有\N戰士掩護就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.79,0:00:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要戰士的掩護是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.96,0:00:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是…潘恩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我現在成了精靈使了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒辦法掩護你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.95,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!既然歐魯索都恢復情感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.85,0:00:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕對要逃出這裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.67,0:00:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想這麼說，但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!是船耶是船耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.99,0:00:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼高興嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全回到孩提時代去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.48,0:00:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的話我可不管喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.87,0:01:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…好痛喔，西莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.60,0:01:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖好乖\N不痛不痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.84,0:01:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽，吃奶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.98,0:01:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有奶啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.61,0:01:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!萊登市正在燒著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.12,0:01:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得要盡快去救他們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.11,0:01:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，這不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.95,0:01:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣下去萊登市會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.72,0:01:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了，潘恩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.48,0:01:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿著那身服裝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.70,0:01:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這非常時期\N還在混什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.43,0:01:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.17,0:01:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是，潘恩等人離開\N燃燒的萊登市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而前往火龍山了，可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎?潘恩啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.25,0:01:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下次\N我就來角色扮演西莉絲吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.76,0:01:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
